    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2>Drug Lords is a strategy game, where you must move from location to location, find the best price to buy and then move to another location till you find the best price to sell your &quot;merchandise&quot;. <br>While you move from one place to another, you will find yourself against random encounters that will help you get more &quot;merchandise&quot;, make you lose it, or challenge you even more, by making you defend your life for it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845290/extras/4f48a04290295bf8c003d532473c6c30.avif?t=1667817417\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845290/extras_big/4f48a04290295bf8c003d532473c6c30.avif?t=1667817417 width=800 height=460 /></span><br>But fear not.<br>You are not alone. you will have your two loyal friends to help you. Scarlet the Sniper and Pete the crazy bomber.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong><u>The Leader</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845290/extras/343865ab0cd6cdcaac3e79fcc892fa20.poster.avif?t=1667817417\" width=247 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845290/extras/343865ab0cd6cdcaac3e79fcc892fa20.webm?t=1667817417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>With A wide arsenal of weapons, the Leader is your many character.  This is the only character that is directly controlled by the player.<br></li><li> <strong><u>Scarlet the Sniper</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845290/extras/6ead7bf95971b5adc2a5dbeb3118230d.poster.avif?t=1667817417\" width=316 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845290/extras/6ead7bf95971b5adc2a5dbeb3118230d.webm?t=1667817417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>With her powerful snipping ability Scarlet will do single target heavy damage to anyone trying to steal your &quot;merchandise&quot; <br></li><li> <strong><u>Pete the crazy bomber</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845290/extras/f14017a1acacb0060a52897357131932.poster.avif?t=1667817417\" width=339 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845290/extras/f14017a1acacb0060a52897357131932.webm?t=1667817417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Heavy area damage is to be expected from Pete. But why Crazy? Can he be trusted?? what will happen if something goes wrong with his contraptions? </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playability</h2>This is a &quot;never ending&quot; game. <br>Everytime you play it, you will get a unique experience, since the events, the prices and the drops will be different.",
